\c 258 
\pc \bd 25\bd*\bd 8\bd*

\s NDABONA IHANGA RITEYE  UBWOBA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ndabona ihanga riteye ubwoba, ndabona ihanga ryiharije, ryavutse murubavu rwa Yesu, ryavutse mu maraso ya Yesu, rifis’intsinzi y’umusaraba, rigize Abami n’Abaherezi\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Ritang’ibimazi nka Abeli ritang’ibimazi nka Eliya./.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’abana b’Imana Ihoraho, n’ihanga ry’Imana yiharije, ryambay’ubwiza bw’Uhoraho, riter’ishari ayandi mahanga,\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ./.uwuhagurutse kurirwanya,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Asanga ariwe yirwanya, asang’ari we yiyica./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndabon’ihanga ritey’ubwoba, rirongorwa n’amasezerano, Balaki ararirwanya arananirwa, Balamu ararivuma arananirwa, umuvumo ku bana b’Imana, uhinduka umuhezagiro ./.Uhinduka umunezero kubw’amasezerano./.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’abana b’Imana Ihoraho, n’ihanga ry’Imana yiharije, ryambay’ubwiza bw’Uhoraho, riter’ishari ayandi mahanga, ./.uwuhagurutse kurirwanya,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Asanga ariwe yirwanya, asang’ari we yiyica./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndabon’ihanga ritey’ubwoba, rirongowe n’Uhoraho, imisozi yose iraribisa, n’inzuzi zose ziraribisa, n’intambwe zose ziraribisa, n’amatanure araribisa\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Ivyo vyose biratinya kubw’inkingi y’umuriro./.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’abana b’Imana Ihoraho, n’ihanga ry’Imana yiharije, ryambay’ubwiza bw’Uhoraho, riter’ishari ayandi mahanga, ./.uwuhagurutse kurirwanya,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Asanga ariwe yirwanya, asang’ari we yiyica./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndabon’ihanga ritey’ubwoba, rica mu nzira ifunganye, ryikoreye imibabaro, ryikoreye umusaraba, riniha iminiho itov\bd*\bd ugwa, rica ahantu h’imbobane ./.\bd*\bd Ku bw’urugendo ruruhije kubw’intambara zinaniza./.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’abana b’Imana Ihoraho, n’ihanga ry’Imana yiharije, ryambay’ubwiza bw’Uhoraho, riter’ishari ayandi mahanga, ./.uwuhagurutse kurirwanya,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Asanga ariwe yirwanya, asang’ari we yiyica./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndabon’ihanga rihambaye, rirwana intambara ziruhije, ritsinda kubw’ukwizera, ritsinda kubw’ivyizigiro, ryuzuye urukundo ruhinguye, iryo niryo ryamaze kurama\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ./.Ritegereje kuruhurwa imibabaro y’igihe gito./.\bd*
\pc \bdit N’abana b’Imana Ihoraho, n’ihanga ry’Imana yiharije, ryambay’ubwiza bw’Uhoraho, riter’ishari ayandi mahanga, ./.uwuhagurutse kurirwanya,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit Asanga ariwe yirwanya, asang’ari we yiyica./.\bdit*
